Document: CircleShape2D  
Path: godot/classes/class_circleshape2d.rst  
Summary: A 2D circle shape used in physics for collision detection with CollisionShape2D nodes.  

Performance: CircleShape2D is fast to check collisions against. It is faster than RectangleShape2D and CapsuleShape2D.
